{"tid":971540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你曾經係tg識左一個女仔而你嬲左佢 入一入黎","createTime":"2019-01-06T16:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T17:57:51.000Z","uid":20731,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"01cf78c6acf02a8047fd8dd298f30f132f21c8c9","tid":971540,"uid":20731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"我知道上次我地見面 <br />\n我拒絕左你 仲自己一個人走左去係令你好失望<br />\n<br />\n我之後鼓起勇氣再搵返你 <br />\n唔知你真係咁嬲我所以咁狠心 定係再怕失望<br />\n你叫我唔好再浪費時間係你身上<br />\n<br />\n直至兩日前我入左院 徘徊係生死邊緣嘅時候<br />\n我先至發現 原來你對我來講 真係好重要<br />\n我唔想失去你 但我已經鼓唔起勇氣再去搵你<br />\n你原諒我 我地重新黎過好嗎？"},{"pid":"10ba661af0d2261873cfd2b0514ea9568cb87e8e","tid":971540,"uid":199162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:58:17.000Z","msg":"唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ee2c02f017562d1054ac1f441e9b235882f256","tid":971540,"uid":11598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"唔喎"},{"pid":"0d9f61e449b10fc5b07fb350c4d4083b439a370b","tid":971540,"uid":172677,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T17:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a4be7727a5f6e05d8f5683a188537f177adcfb","tid":971540,"uid":37736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T17:00:40.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接打呢段俾佢睇而要打上黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99239f1273db2fe92e94b792b5bc93a1cc391454","tid":971540,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"我地一個am 一個fm<br />\n都唔岩channel既<br />\n緣已盡啦"},{"pid":"29ffaaa07d5e3253ca2c2f198b46f48ecea61383","tid":971540,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主分享笑話一則"},{"pid":"93149fcc8972922f777995c29702b4b3a2451115","tid":971540,"uid":34511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply